it.csi.mddtools.guigen

Interface PanelDef

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier

    public interface PanelDef
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Panel Def'. Definizione di pannello riusabile. Deve essere definita in un modello esterno e referenziata tramite l'oggetto PanelDefUse.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Panel
    • Params
    • App Data Defs
    • Type Defs
    • Roles
    • Actors
    • Use Cases
    • On Refresh Command
    • States
    • Default State
    See Also:
    GuigenPackage.getPanelDef()
